{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8ad68094-42c4-43ba-88c6-3115cbf963cb","content":"Here's the recommended setup:\n\n### 1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`)\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.7\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\nThat's it — `MSTest.Sdk` bundles the test runner, framework, and analyzers automatically. No `<PackageReference>` items needed.\n\n### 2. Enable parallel execution\n\nAdd an assembly-level attribute (e.g. in a `Setup.cs` at the project root):\n\n```csharp\nusing Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting;\n\n[assembly: Parallelize(Scope = ExecutionScope.MethodLevel)]\n```\n\n`MethodLevel` runs all test methods in parallel. Use `ClassLevel` if you want methods within a single class to run sequentially but classes to run in parallel.\n\n### 3. Run database tests sequentially\n\nMark your database test class with `[DoNotParallelize]`:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Can_Insert_Record() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Can_Query_Records() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\nTests in that class will run **after** all parallelizable tests complete, and they will execute **one at a time**.\n\n### Summary\n\n| Concern | Mechanism |\n|---|---|\n| Minimal project file | `MSTest.Sdk` (replaces all boilerplate) |\n| Parallel by default | `[assembly: Parallelize]` |\n| Sequential exceptions | `[DoNotParallelize]` on class |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"65b37555-4ec8-4233-ace0-79376ad98579","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The directory is empty. The user is just asking for guidance on setting up an MSTest project. Let me provide the recommended setup based on my knowledge of MSTest.Sdk, parallel execution, and the `[DoNotParallelize]` attribute.","outputTokens":497,"requestId":"E3C6:182BD0:18CD06A:1BC6486:6A052B2D"},"id":"bc41d93c-5d21-4542-a86b-e7e00a16550a","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:54:01.048Z","parentId":"3780c9fc-f6a1-474f-8af7-764c9402e6a8"}
